{"tid":1238654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線警察早安","createTime":"2019-06-18T01:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T02:44:14.000Z","uid":86610,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fe7738ab98a0d938fbe44bc3f53b1826608254da","tid":1238654,"uid":86610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:43:27.000Z","msg":"尋日盧一哥已經將大部分既責任推卸到前線指揮官，即係佢唔會再保你地，只係保佢自己。<br />\n<br />\n加上胡亂地定性暴亂，騷亂，依家又話小部分人暴亂，變相你地放左150枚催淚彈，20發橡膠彈，歐打已經無力反抗既示威者，都已經被佢推得一乾二淨。<br />\n<br />\n好快，前線既警員就會好似[<span style=\"color: red;\">size=6]暗角7警[/size=6]</span>咁，只會幫你請律師，然後等你地自生自滅，再去捧呢一班人出來，你地甘心咩。<br />\n<br />\n要自保自己就係要將前線落既order 做好記錄，將呢d重要證供發放比傳媒，咁樣你地先有機會。<br />\n<br />\n最後，好知為之。"},{"pid":"f72a7d7b88585043bc6057e9abf1c0f2071593f3","tid":1238654,"uid":186911,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:44:11.000Z","msg":"支持香港警察同高層割蓆"},{"pid":"8917d6ac91b2ac70d33b07f312d5182c81cb58d0","tid":1238654,"uid":86610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:44:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59f61d0cb6c21a412a65dbac4f35f0a1ede43a7f","tid":1238654,"uid":43553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:45:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f93da32f730a0565e4a4e1ac394d180b3ca8818a","tid":1238654,"uid":86610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:45:28.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"80920c2d7450e4d79bfe9763200f806fd64784f7","tid":1238654,"uid":86610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:47:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3ce464aa397867d389242272e0155ac8cfb7d80f","tid":1238654,"uid":86610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:47:44.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8f70ecee81174b4422f3b1e70368f69a299bd826","tid":1238654,"uid":186961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe7738ab98a0d938fbe44bc3f53b1826608254da","tid":1238654,"uid":86610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:43:27.000Z","msg":"尋日盧一哥已經將大部分既責任推卸到前線指揮官，即係佢唔會再保你地，只係保佢自己。<br />\n<br />\n加上胡亂地定性暴亂，騷亂，依家又話小部分人暴亂，變相你地放左150枚催淚彈，20發橡膠彈，歐打已經無力反抗既示威者，都已經被佢推得一乾二淨。<br />\n<br />\n好快，前線既警員就會好似[<span style=\"color: red;\">size=6]暗角7警[/size=6]</span>咁，只會幫你請律師，然後等你地自生自滅，再去捧呢一班人出來，你地甘心咩。<br />\n<br />\n要自保自己就係要將前線落既order 做好記錄，將呢d重要證供發放比傳媒，咁樣你地先有機會。<br />\n<br />\n最後，好知為之。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:47:50.000Z","msg":"我就唔樂觀喇,<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣就話全個警隊得七個人+朱經緯八個人有事,<br />\n梗係可以話全力支援, 有錢有律師幫手啦<br />\n<br />\n但而家咁多人出事, 警務署署長又玩語言藝術同前線割𥱊,<br />\n點會有咁多支援啊"},{"pid":"81f316249632832718a17e1f6ba137899802b061","tid":1238654,"uid":86610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:48:13.000Z","msg":"pisg"},{"pid":"a5d3b66ddaae445deffa19288f2a124557ddbd0d","tid":1238654,"uid":86610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:48:23.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8083dae104d5dcb29a07314ea4acd870a87997f8","tid":1238654,"uid":180228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:48:36.000Z","msg":"棄暗投明<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"9e127924354d03d6d557d5076728a1497eb6ae07","tid":1238654,"uid":86610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:49:19.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0da6a19de464f0f518f714de7b953889dde92ba0","tid":1238654,"uid":86610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:51:12.000Z","msg":"推到比人知"},{"pid":"f0a633879f7a426874ae10deb2e3a0553f34c3f8","tid":1238654,"uid":86610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:51:25.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"c3a1b10b6ee99ae20bcd87b245d2ab64ce13abb1","tid":1238654,"uid":86610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T01:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm